sequenceDiagram
    actor Teacher
    participant UI as React Import Wizard
    participant API as ASP.NET Core API
    participant Parser as Excel Parser
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    Teacher->>UI: Upload .xlsx
    UI->>API: POST import-preview
    API->>API: Verify ownership and file rules
    API->>Parser: Parse and normalize rows
    Parser-->>API: Parsed rows
    API->>DB: Resolve users and enrollments in batches
    DB-->>API: Matches
    API->>DB: Save batch and preview outcomes
    API-->>UI: Counts and paged preview
    Teacher->>UI: Confirm valid rows
    UI->>API: POST imports/{batchId}/confirm
    API->>DB: Re-check and transactionally enroll
    DB-->>API: Commit
    API-->>UI: Final result and report link
